description._content: Title: Royal Aircraft Factory, Catalog #: sdasm_00089413 Manufacturer: Royal Aircraft Factory Notes: This isn't an S.E.5. Note that it is a two-seater, with a large rudder and rear cockpit. The engine installation is similar to an S.E.5 but the rest of the aircraft appears to have other elements of Royal Aircraft Factory designs, most notably the late production B.E.2d and R.E.8 types.
